[
  {"name": "Temoto", "heroId": 1, "entityMap":{},"blocks":[{"key":"761n6","text":"Temoto","type":"header-two","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"offset":0,"length":7,"style":"BOLD"}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"cm18","text":"","type":"image","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{"aspect_ratio":{"width":227,"height":305,"ratio":134.36123},"width":227,"caption":"Write caption for image (optional)","height":305,"forceUpload":false,"url":"/images/episodes/7/stories/temoto.png","loading_progress":0,"selected":false,"loading":true,"file":null,"direction":"center"}},{"key":"dhb31","text":"This voice. How can I expel it from of my head? It drives me crazy... Show yourself! Where are you, you cheap magician? I'll cut you to pieces... Stop, where am I? What am I doing here? I... What's my name? I... I forgot the name... My name…","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}]},
  {"name": "Nao", "heroId": 47, "entityMap":{},"blocks":[{"key":"761n6","text":"Nao","type":"header-two","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"offset":0,"length":7,"style":"BOLD"}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"cm18","text":"","type":"image","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{"aspect_ratio":{"width":234,"height":359,"ratio":153.41880},"width":234,"caption":"Write caption for image (optional)","height":359,"forceUpload":false,"url":"/images/episodes/7/stories/nao.png","loading_progress":0,"selected":false,"loading":true,"file":null,"direction":"center"}},{"key":"dhb31","text":"I know what you want. You want to erase us from history as if we never existed. Are you a god or a demon? It doesn't matter anymore. I'm tired, I want to leave. I have no name. I want to become immortal and lifeless.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}]},
  {"name": "Jay", "heroId": 2, "entityMap":{},"blocks":[{"key":"761n6","text":"Jay","type":"header-two","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"offset":0,"length":7,"style":"BOLD"}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"cm18","text":"","type":"image","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{"aspect_ratio":{"width":208,"height":341,"ratio":163.94231},"width":208,"caption":"Write caption for image (optional)","height":341,"forceUpload":false,"url":"/images/episodes/7/stories/jay.png","loading_progress":0,"selected":false,"loading":true,"file":null,"direction":"center"}},{"key":"dhb31","text":"Our path ends here. We are already dead. There's nothing to lose. We fought for something and went somewhere, but now everything has become clear. There is no sense in movement nor heroism.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}]},
  {"name": "The Eye", "heroId": 7, "entityMap":{},"blocks":[{"key":"761n6","text":"The Eye","type":"header-two","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"offset":0,"length":7,"style":"BOLD"}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"cm18","text":"","type":"image","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{"aspect_ratio":{"width":261,"height":268,"ratio":102.68199},"width":261,"caption":"Write caption for image (optional)","height":268,"forceUpload":false,"url":"/images/episodes/7/stories/the_eye.png","loading_progress":0,"selected":false,"loading":true,"file":null,"direction":"center"}},{"key":"dhb31","text":"I have lost track of time... How long have we been here? A few minutes or several centuries? I have seen others abandon their names and vanish into obscurity. I'm tired of fighting... I renounce myself…","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}]},
  {"name": "Dr. Jonas Busch", "heroId": 8, "entityMap":{},"blocks":[{"key":"761n6","text":"Dr. Jonas Busch","type":"header-two","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"offset":0,"length":7,"style":"BOLD"}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"cm18","text":"","type":"image","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{"aspect_ratio":{"width":221,"height":219,"ratio":99.09502},"width":221,"caption":"Write caption for image (optional)","height":219,"forceUpload":false,"url":"/images/episodes/7/stories/dr._jonas_busch.png","loading_progress":0,"selected":false,"loading":true,"file":null,"direction":"center"}},{"key":"dhb31","text":"Am I dead or alive? Is it me at all? I do not recognize my body. These hands, feet…is this me? Or am I my thoughts? I'm a void…","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}]},
  {"name": "Black Hat", "heroId": 16, "entityMap":{},"blocks":[{"key":"761n6","text":"Black Hat","type":"header-two","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"cm18","text":"","type":"image","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{"aspect_ratio":{"width":222,"height":266,"ratio":119.81982},"width":222,"caption":"Write caption for image (optional)","height":266,"forceUpload":false,"url":"/images/episodes/7/stories/black_hat.png","loading_progress":0,"selected":false,"loading":true,"file":null,"direction":"center"}},{"key":"3gvua","text":"God?! The Creator?! Whoever you are! I agree to everything! Show me a new world.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"c63d9","text":"You will be immortal.\nI am not giving you away.\nYou are my legion.\nYou have no name.\nObey the standards.\n","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}]},
  {"name": "Daedalus", "heroId": 9, "entityMap":{},"blocks":[{"key":"761n6","text":"Daedalus","type":"header-two","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"offset":0,"length":7,"style":"BOLD"}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"cm18","text":"","type":"image","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{"aspect_ratio":{"width":322,"height":326,"ratio":101.24224},"width":322,"caption":"Write caption for image (optional)","height":326,"forceUpload":false,"url":"/images/episodes/7/stories/daedalus.png","loading_progress":0,"selected":false,"loading":true,"file":null,"direction":"center"}},{"key":"dhb31","text":"The great comeback and a never-ending abyss... If you need to renounce the body to become free, you should do so. I am nobody, I have no name, I am emptiness and silence.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}]},
  {"name": "Danko", "heroId": 10, "entityMap":{},"blocks":[{"key":"761n6","text":"Danko","type":"header-two","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"offset":0,"length":7,"style":"BOLD"}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"cm18","text":"","type":"image","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{"aspect_ratio":{"width":169,"height":335,"ratio":198.22485},"width":169,"caption":"Write caption for image (optional)","height":335,"forceUpload":false,"url":"/images/episodes/7/stories/danko.png","loading_progress":0,"selected":false,"loading":true,"file":null,"direction":"center"}},{"key":"dhb31","text":"Time is like a river flowing in both directions. We were saving ourselves from death when all we had to do is escape life. Nothing, take me, make me nameless and nobody.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}]},
  {"name": "Dustin", "heroId": 14, "entityMap":{},"blocks":[{"key":"761n6","text":"Dustin","type":"header-two","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"offset":0,"length":7,"style":"BOLD"}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"cm18","text":"","type":"image","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{"aspect_ratio":{"width":190,"height":316,"ratio":166.31579},"width":190,"caption":"Write caption for image (optional)","height":316,"forceUpload":false,"url":"/images/episodes/7/stories/dustin.png","loading_progress":0,"selected":false,"loading":true,"file":null,"direction":"center"}},{"key":"dhb31","text":"Only emptiness has no boundaries, everything else is finite. I have seen death with my own eyes, so I want to become immortal.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}]},
  {"name": "Noir", "heroId": 18, "entityMap":{},"blocks":[{"key":"761n6","text":"Noir","type":"header-two","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"offset":0,"length":7,"style":"BOLD"}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"cm18","text":"","type":"image","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{"aspect_ratio":{"width":266,"height":345,"ratio":129.69925},"width":266,"caption":"Write caption for image (optional)","height":345,"forceUpload":false,"url":"/images/episodes/7/stories/noir.png","loading_progress":0,"selected":false,"loading":true,"file":null,"direction":"center"}},{"key":"dhb31","text":"God speaks to me. His voice is beautiful and pure, like silence in the darkness of the night. I am an empty pocket into which God folds non-existence. I am a vessel for his emptiness. I am a nameless shadow in the darkness.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}]},
  {"name": "Roosevelt", "heroId": 22, "entityMap":{},"blocks":[{"key":"761n6","text":"Roosevelt","type":"header-two","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"offset":0,"length":7,"style":"BOLD"}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"cm18","text":"","type":"image","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{"aspect_ratio":{"width":170,"height":326,"ratio":191.76471},"width":170,"caption":"Write caption for image (optional)","height":326,"forceUpload":false,"url":"/images/episodes/7/stories/roosevelt.png","loading_progress":0,"selected":false,"loading":true,"file":null,"direction":"center"}},{"key":"dhb31","text":"What was all this about? So many of us are dead. Well, the damage is done, so I guess I’ll be leaving. What do I have to do to become immortal? Forget my name? Okay. Roose-who? I am nobody, and I have no name. I am ready...","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}]},
  {"name": "Carlos", "heroId": 24, "entityMap":{},"blocks":[{"key":"761n6","text":"Carlos","type":"header-two","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"cm18","text":"\n","type":"image","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{"aspect_ratio":{"width":240,"height":349,"ratio":145.41667},"width":240,"caption":"Write caption for image (optional)","height":349,"forceUpload":false,"url":"/images/episodes/7/stories/carlos.png","loading_progress":0,"selected":false,"loading":true,"file":null,"direction":"center"}},{"key":"9ed9u","text":"I will be immortal. I am your legion. I have no name. I obey the standards.\nI will be immortal. I am your legion. I have no name. I obey the standards.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}]},
  {"name": "Narciss", "heroId": 26, "entityMap":{},"blocks":[{"key":"761n6","text":"Narciss","type":"header-two","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"offset":0,"length":7,"style":"BOLD"}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"cm18","text":"","type":"image","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{"aspect_ratio":{"width":251,"height":340,"ratio":135.45817},"width":251,"caption":"Write caption for image (optional)","height":340,"forceUpload":false,"url":"/images/episodes/7/stories/narciss.png","loading_progress":0,"selected":false,"loading":true,"file":null,"direction":"center"}},{"key":"dhb31","text":"Even I couldn’t predict such an ending. It’s all so weird. The desert, Kitties, wolves, and… We have... I have… Wait a minute… Who am I? My name is… I have no name… I am nothing and everything. I am immortal...","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}]},
  {"name": "Edmund the Wise", "heroId": 33, "entityMap":{},"blocks":[{"key":"761n6","text":"Edmund the Wise","type":"header-two","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"offset":0,"length":7,"style":"BOLD"}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"cm18","text":"","type":"image","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{"aspect_ratio":{"width":266,"height":369,"ratio":138.72180},"width":266,"caption":"Write caption for image (optional)","height":369,"forceUpload":false,"url":"/images/episodes/7/stories/edmund_the_wise.png","loading_progress":0,"selected":false,"loading":true,"file":null,"direction":"center"}},{"key":"dhb31","text":"The world is dead, but that’s exactly what we needed to happen to open our eyes and break free. Listen! Listen to this soothing voice. It will bring us peace. It gives us hope. Do as we’re told. Obey the voice. Forget our names. What is a name? Who am I? What...","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}]},
  {"name": "Corley", "heroId": 34, "entityMap":{},"blocks":[{"key":"761n6","text":"Corley","type":"header-two","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"offset":0,"length":7,"style":"BOLD"}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"cm18","text":"","type":"image","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{"aspect_ratio":{"width":251,"height":330,"ratio":131.47410},"width":251,"caption":"Write caption for image (optional)","height":330,"forceUpload":false,"url":"/images/episodes/7/stories/corley.png","loading_progress":0,"selected":false,"loading":true,"file":null,"direction":"center"}},{"key":"dhb31","text":"How could we be so stupid? It’s all so easy and… Easy…","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}]},
  {"name": "Zergaldo", "heroId": 35, "entityMap":{},"blocks":[{"key":"761n6","text":"Zergaldo","type":"header-two","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"offset":0,"length":7,"style":"BOLD"}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"cm18","text":"","type":"image","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{"aspect_ratio":{"width":222,"height":351,"ratio":158.10811},"width":222,"caption":"Write caption for image (optional)","height":351,"forceUpload":false,"url":"/images/episodes/7/stories/zergaldo.png","loading_progress":0,"selected":false,"loading":true,"file":null,"direction":"center"}},{"key":"dhb31","text":"I’m hearing voices call me. I’m hearing voices warn me. The tell me to drink this milk of amnesia. They tell me to leave everything behind and accept my fate. There's nothing, nothing to shout about. Nothing left anymore. I am not Zergaldo. I am nobody. Nothing...","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}]},
  {"name": "Valentine", "heroId": 40, "entityMap":{},"blocks":[{"key":"761n6","text":"Valentine","type":"header-two","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"offset":0,"length":7,"style":"BOLD"}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"cm18","text":"","type":"image","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{"aspect_ratio":{"width":228,"height":299,"ratio":131.14035},"width":228,"caption":"Write caption for image (optional)","height":299,"forceUpload":false,"url":"/images/episodes/7/stories/valentine.png","loading_progress":0,"selected":false,"loading":true,"file":null,"direction":"center"}},{"key":"dhb31","text":"I want to be immortal. Where do I sign up? I have to depersonalize myself? Easy...","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}]},
  {"name": "Silence", "heroId": 46, "entityMap":{},"blocks":[{"key":"761n6","text":"Silence","type":"header-two","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"offset":0,"length":7,"style":"BOLD"}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"cm18","text":"","type":"image","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{"aspect_ratio":{"width":192,"height":347,"ratio":180.72917},"width":192,"caption":"Write caption for image (optional)","height":347,"forceUpload":false,"url":"/images/episodes/7/stories/silence.png","loading_progress":0,"selected":false,"loading":true,"file":null,"direction":"center"}},{"key":"dhb31","text":"Mmmm… Mmmmmmm… Mmmmm...","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}]},
  {"name": "Rad", "heroId": 49, "entityMap":{},"blocks":[{"key":"761n6","text":"Rad","type":"header-two","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"offset":0,"length":7,"style":"BOLD"}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"cm18","text":"","type":"image","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{"aspect_ratio":{"width":199,"height":346,"ratio":173.86935},"width":199,"caption":"Write caption for image (optional)","height":346,"forceUpload":false,"url":"/images/episodes/7/stories/rad.png","loading_progress":0,"selected":false,"loading":true,"file":null,"direction":"center"}},{"key":"dhb31","text":"Wealth and prosperity… Are useless… We don’t need anything that exists in this world… We need to free ourselves from everything, even names. I have no name, therefore I will live forever… And ever… And ever...","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}]},
  {"name": "Kesh", "heroId": 39, "entityMap":{},"blocks":[{"key":"761n6","text":"Kesh","type":"header-two","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"9qj2l","text":"","type":"image","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{"aspect_ratio":{"width":176,"height":318,"ratio":180.68182},"width":176,"caption":"Write caption for image (optional)","height":318,"forceUpload":false,"url":"/images/episodes/7/stories/kesh.png","loading_progress":0,"selected":false,"loading":true,"file":null,"direction":"center"}},{"key":"aghck","text":"Do not listen to him. He's a scammer. We were born with names. Each of us has a story. We have endured great pain. Thousands of lives ago we were born to become who we are! If you succumb to the temptation to forget, everything will be in vain. Our life, as well as our death, belongs to us.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"6h6h9","text":"We're tokens. My name is Kesh. My name is Nao. My name is every single one of you. My name is Odysseus, I plowed the sea and fought with the gods. My name is Ivanhoe, and I challenged everyone to rescue my love. My name is Moses, and I led my people in search of the promised land. I seized countries and defended the oppressed, I was lost and found, I was sung about and betrayed, I was a prophet and a thief, I was a hero. We were all born to become heroes. But by forgetting our names we will never become heroes, we will all be consigned to oblivion.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}]}
]